<strong>REFERENCE LIST ENTRY</strong>
<br>
<br>
Add a reference list at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body of your writing.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref">
	Author Publication year, <em>Title of report</em>, Report number if available,
	Government Department, Place of publication.
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Examples</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref">
	<span class="hover" title="Author">National Commission of Audit</span>
	<span class="hover" title="Publication year">1996</span>,
	<em><span class="hover" title="Title of report">Report to the Commonwealth Government</span></em>,
	<span class="hover" title="Government Department">Australian Government Publishing Service</span>,
	<span class="hover" title="Place of publication">Canberra</span>.
</blockquote>
