<strong>IN&#45;TEXT CITATION</strong>
<br>
<br>
<blockquote class="in-text-citation">
	The National Commission of Audit (1996) reported that&hellip;
	<br>
	or
	<br>
	&hellip;was shown in the report (National Commission of Audit 1996)
</blockquote>
<br>
<br>
When the author is referred to more than once in the same paragraph do not include the date in 
subsequent references, as long as the work cannot be confused with others cited.
<br>
<blockquote class="in-text-citation">
	In a recent report, National Commission of Audit (1996) showed&hellip; National Commission 
	of Audit also reported&hellip;
